      { "q": "Order from smallest to largest: $\\tfrac{1}{2}, \\tfrac{5}{12}, \\tfrac{2}{3}, \\tfrac{1}{4}$ (use twelfths).", "a": "$\\tfrac{1}{4}, \\tfrac{5}{12}, \\tfrac{1}{2}, \\tfrac{2}{3}$",
